  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Central Restaurant</strong> is where you'll eat if you've booked half board. Breakfast is served from 7.30am to 10am and has plenty of hot and cold options. The buffet has a chef station where they cook eggs to order. Dinner is buffet style with different stations serving a wide range of dishes. There's a gala dinner with waiter service once a week. </p>
<p><strong>La Vineria del Colle</strong> specialises in local food and has an incredible wine list to go with it. This is payable locally with a discount for Inghams guests.</p>
<p>Free tea and biscuits are served every day from from 4.30pm to 5.30pm.</p>
<p>Christmas gala included with live music</p>
<p>New Year's Eve gala dinner included with champagne and music.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
