  <description><![CDATA[<p>Grand Hotel Sestriere has great facilities and an even better location. The lifts are only a few minutes away and you can get to them easily with the free shuttle available at selected times. The centre of town is a short walk away and you can look forward to some great mountain views when you get back to the hotel - we recommend enjoying them from the bar. You can pick from over 1,500 wine labels and sit next to the open fire.</p>
<p>There's two restaurants here so you can change things up and upgrade to à la carte for a couple of nights. If you've got some spare time, head for the spa and check out the sauna, steam room and whirlpool (payable locally).</p>]]></description>
